snippet.textDisplay: This girl was not as talented as Saveria, but somehow she gets through, mostly by her persistance.  People are saying how it proves the show is rigged, but I don't believe this proves it one way or the other.  It was obvious that neither Luke nor Lionel were feeling it with her at all, so they voted no. If the show was rigged, Katy's temper tantrum would have been planned and a fake, but every account I have read about it says it was true, she was pissed. I don't particularly agree with any of them except Katy has a point because they have let a lot of contestants with a lot less talent and ability than Saveria go through, so for that reason I agree with Katy that she deserved a ticket to Hollywood.  But when judging talent in any type of competition, it is always very subjective.  I just think they need to be more consistent, and also if one person gets a second chance than everyone who is marginal should get one.
